phrases: A key to what, I wonder.
Could it have something to do with my promise?
What are you doing up there?
You have not had anything to eat since coming home.
Uh, do you know where I met my first love?
I could probably find out if I looked into it.
I just feel like checking it out.
Can you arrange for a ride tomorrow?
We do not have school, remember?
I am really curious about that promise,
but there is no way I am missing out on such a fun school activity!
We are getting on the buses.
Why is she looking so uncomfortable?
Hey, tell me, Bean Sprout, what does she mean by groups?
You were sleeping when we picked groups.
Each group's six students, and ours...
do not you think you are clinging to Mistress a little too much?
Although, I do appreciate how you feel about me!
Hey, do not push me, Ruri-chan!
I cannot believe this is happening!
You set me up, did not you?!
If looks could kill, I would be dead right now!
Onodera's shoulder is up against me.
My heart will not stop pounding!
I will bet you she can hear it too!
What am I going to do?
I wonder if Ichijou-kun can hear my heart throbbing?
No, no, no, no, you are fine!
Hey, darling, get off me, will you?
Hey, Ichijou Raku, do not you think you are getting a little too carried away?
Looks like you want to go to hell before we even reach our destination, huh?
After repeating this kind of exchange forty times or so,
Well, it did have its perks, but...
I set up that road trip for you!
In terms of positive or negative, I would rate it positive,
but I want to pound your face in!
I hope Ichijou-kun did not think I was a nuisance.
You guys are going to get started on the rice and curry.
Onodera and Miyamoto, could you go get some firewood for us?
My first field trip and sleepover with everyone!
I do want to find out more about my first love,
but for now, I think I will just enjoy myself!
What took you so long, Kirisaki-san?
Kirisaki sure looks like she is having a ball.
Well, she is always been the type to get all excited
I will bet she is happy beyond belief right now!
The boy I made a promise with ten years ago, huh?
Even if I did run into him again, I would not recognize him, would I?
Hey, just leave it to me!
Oh, but he might still have that scar on his forehead from that day.
That is the only thing I have to go on, huh?
The whole thing's a huge mystery to me.
I never did figure out what Onodera's key was really for.
Just who was the boy that she made a promise with ten years ago?
Hey, Bean Sprout, I need more hot water for this pot
Jeez, will you watch your step?
It is just like the little boy's!
I get the feeling that I have seen it somewhere before.
Hey, Bean Sprout, how did you get that scar on your forehead?
I have had it since I was a kid... but how did I get it?
I used to pet a lot of animals, see.
I guess I got attacked by one of them.
Wait, what the heck am I thinking?
There is no way that they are the same person!
And did not he say so himself?
The girl he promised gave him a locket as a symbol of their reunion.
He has nothing to do with my promise!
This is our room for tonight, huh?
It is bigger than we expected, is not it?
Our school definitely is not stingy when it comes to these things.
To add to that, even though there is a sliding door between us,
we get to sleep in the same room as the girls!
I am so glad that I enrolled in this school!
By the way, Maiko-kun, where are you sleeping the balcony or the hallway?
I cannot sleep in the room?!
Onodera and I are both sleeping in this room?
Ugh, that makes me all the more nervous.
I heard this inn has a hot spring.
Let us take a bath together!
Have you ever bathed in a hot spring before, Chitoge?
I have always wanted to try!
I-I have never taken a bath with multiple people before.
I thought Kirisaki was acting a little strange before,
but I guess I was reading too much into it.
Now then, what do you guys want to do?
We still have some free time left.
Since we are all here, want to play cards or something?
Also, normal rules would not be any fun,
so how about a penalty for the losers?
The loser has to reveal her three sizes
Okay then, the color of her panties
What she thinks are her sexiest parts
Which part of her body she washes first
She tells us the story of... her first love... or something.
The story of my first love?
Dammit Shuu, did you forget that my first love might be Onodera?
As far as my first love goes...
I have no proof, but it is probably...
I have not really fallen in love!
Okay, let us get this game of Old Maid started!
I am totally cool with this, all right?
I cannot afford to worry about others now.
You can read her like a book!
That one's got to be the joker!
It is written all over her face.
Why is she making that face?
It has to be the joker!
I am going to regret this!
What the hell's that tragic look for?
How desperate are you not to lose?
Hey, everything's written on your face.
Would it kill you to put on your poker face?
Our couple's going to duke it out!
Sorry, but you are just going to have to let me win.
So this one's not the joker, huh?
I cannot afford to lose, either.
Damn, I feel like a coward for beating her like this.
She realized that I took her joker on purpose, huh?
But this makes us even, right?
After this, whether I win or lose...
You were supposed to show up ages ago!
Come on, let us head to the bath.
You sure you are not trying to say, Let us peep on the girls!?
And besides, I hear that the boys and girls are bathing at different times.
You have got a phone call at the front desk!
I hope he is not up to one of his evil schemes again.
Let us go get ready for our baths, too!
Oh, crap, I am supposed to be in the bath by now.
As of today, your social life is over!
Now that I think of it, I never got to hear about anyone's first love today.
It would have been cool to hear about Onodera's.
Whatever, this hot spring feels great!
The atmosphere here feels like heaven!
Where do you get off doing a butterfly stroke in a hot spring!?
What the hell do you think you are doing?
What are you doing in the men's bath?
Anyway, I am going to let you off this time,
but you need to get yourself out of here!
Sorry, I owe you big time!
And do not look this way!
I-I have never done anything like this before.
You are not supposed to bring your towel into the spring.
It is a lot bigger than we thought, huh?
Uh, what do I do now?
You can take that thing off first!
Stop wandering around, and wash your body.
Serves you right, you goddamn punk!
As of tonight, you will forever be stigmatized as a pervert and a Peeping Tom,
and you will spend the rest of your youth isolated in the darkness!
Are you done with your bath already?
I just could not help myself and went ahead!
No, we need to scrub that body first!
Was not there another girl with you just now?
No, no, I am by myself!
I mean, I was the first one in!
Do not stand up when you shower!
Here, use this to hide yourself for now.
Kirisaki, you are helping me out?
What other choice do I have?
You are supposed to be my boyfriend, after all.
If it ever gets out that you came into the girls' bath to peep on us,
You and I will have to spend the next three years as the object of everyone is scorn.
In short, if they catch you, we are both toast!
I will back you up, but you have to come up with a way to escape somehow.
That is easy for you to say!
Onodera and the other girls are blocking the entrance!
On the other hand, the fences are too high for me to even think about climbing over.
Okay, why do not we help each other wash?
After all, it does not seem like Tsugumi-san's used to Japanese baths.
N-No, that will not be necess
Now, now, where do you want me to scrub you?
Unfortunately, I could not find any good spots to look from,
but just listening leaves a lot to the imagination, would not you say?
Mmm, got to hand it to you, Maiko!
Still, Raku's pretty late to the party.
What is taking him so long?
Well, he did get some special treatment in that bus.
All right, the door's straight ahead.
All I need is an opportunity.
I see a tanuki over there!
Hey, it is a lot bigger than I expected!
I am so jealous of adults and their bodies!
Heh, want to cop a feel?
If she catches me now, there will be totally serious hell to pay!
Scorn from my classmates will be the least of my problems!
Worst case scenario, I could be... expelled!
Hey, so where is the tanuki?
The exit's getting farther and farther away!
At this point, my only hope is to hang around and hide until the girls' bathing time ends.
For a tomboy, you have got a seriously hot body.
Why is your skin so silky smooth?
Now expulsion seems tame in comparison!
If I am caught, I will be...
J-Just hide behind me for now!
I am going to be frank, how far have you two gone?
You two have been dating openly for quite some time now.
We were thinking that you must be pretty far along by now.
But then again, you both still call each other by your last names.
Never mind that, have not you ever wondered what Tsugumi's first love was like?
Wh-What I am experiencing is not love!
All right, while they are caught up in their girl talk,
I have got to find an escape route, no matter what!
The men's bath should be on the other side.
Does that hole connect the two baths?
Now if I could just make it over there somehow...
I will divert their attention, so you hurry over to that hole!
We do not need to talk about me.
What kind of boy do you have a crush on, Onodera-sama?
Dera-chan, you are crushing on someone?
N-No, I do not have a crush!
You told me about him before!
But she said she did not have one the other day!
Why are you just sitting there?!
D-Damn it, I want to hear this!
Right now, my first priority is getting out of here!
If I say there is no one, then there is no one!
Who thought that my last escape route would be blocked by the most formidable wall!?
C-Come on, Kosaki-chan, I would like you to tell me too!
I think I just felt something soft underneath.
Come on, what are you doing?
What was that sound just now?
You do not think they realized we have been eavesdropping here?
What the hell are you doing there?
I was just holding my breath underwater.
Hey, man, you need get on in this!
Nah, I am going to take five.
I know that you were not to blame for any of that today.
But how much of a klutz can you be?!
I am a victim, too, you know.
You saw my perfect body, did not you?!
I cannot believe that you of all people would see me stark naked!
I-I did not see anything, okay?
I mean, that place was pretty steamy!
You are telling the truth, right?
If you are lying, I swear
Then what about that last thing?
What do you mean, that last thing?
If you do not get it, then never mind.
Of course I could never say it.
All righty, tomorrow we are all heading to the mountain!
If you open that sliding door, you are a dead man.
I will not, I will not!
Damn right we are opening it!
